Rating: 4
This was incredible. I had never really cooked lamb before and what's more challenging, I used thick cut lamb chops. I did what my mother told me and just cooked the lamb for a little longer (not more than 15) than the receipe stated. My partner loves lamb and olive anything he almost did a face plant into this dish. I must admit it made me look like an gourmet chef and it was really easy to make!!! The secret is the presentation. This is a stunning smelling dish as it cooks but what will "WOW" everyone is the presentation.

