THIS IS REALLY DELICIOUS BUT I HAVE TWO RECOMMENDATIONS. 1) MAKE THE LAMB CHOPS SEPARATELY (GRILLED, PAN FRIED OR WHATEVER) BECAUSE IT'S MUCH EASIER TO ENSURE THEY COME OUT TO YOUR DESIRED DONENESS. 2) DOUBLE THE TOMATO, FETA AND OLIVE AMOUNTS. IT'S THE STAR HERE.

