This is delicious, and a good prepare-ahead dish for a dinner party. Next time I will brown the lamb chops before roasting them, which would make for a more attractive presentation. Also, I tossed the tomatoes, olives and cheese with the potatoes to warm and soften the cheese a bit. I've served the potatoes with a rack of lamb, and think they would be good with just about any roast - they are full of flavor!

