Rating: 4
I did a variation of the recipe on the grill. It was fabulous. I did the potatoes in an old foil pan and add just a little more oil. Cook for about 50 minutes. Pierce them with a fork to tell if done. I also grilled the chops over medium heat on a gas grill for 20 minutes turning every four minutes. The taste combination of the feta & the olives was exquisite with lamb. A refreshing change from the good old grilled chops and mint sauce.

